data.oai_dc:dc: RW scores (for each caviomorph genera) obtained through a Generalized Procrustes Analysis of the landmarks plus semilandmarks dataset (SL). Archive format: .nts. Semilandmarks were slid using a minimum bending energy criterion with 5 iterations. Data generated using tpsRelW 1.46 (Rohlf, 2008. Available at: http://life.bio.sunysb.edu/morph/)
